-- ‡∏ñ‡πâ‡∏≤‡∏°‡∏µ API Key ‡∏≠‡∏¢‡∏π‡πà‡πÅ‡∏•‡πâ‡∏ß ‡πÉ‡∏´‡πâ‡πÄ‡∏õ‡∏¥‡∏î‡∏´‡∏ô‡πâ‡∏≤‡πÅ‡∏ä‡∏ó‡∏ó‡∏±‡∏ô‡∏ó‡∏µ
if GroqAPI.API_KEY and GroqAPI.API_KEY ~= "" then
    apiScreen.Visible = false
    chatScreen.Visible = true
    clearChat()
else
    chatScreen.Visible = false
    apiScreen.Visible = true
end

